  "prompt": "Why do many celebrities decide to wear purity rings?",
  "response": "Purity rings are a symbol of a commitment to abstain from sexual activity until marriage. Many celebrities decide to wear purity rings for a variety of reasons. Some do it as a personal commitment to their religious beliefs or moral values, while others may do it to make a public statement or as part of a broader campaign promoting abstinence. Wearing a purity ring can also be a way for celebrities to connect with their fans who share similar values or to set an example for young people. Ultimately, the decision to wear a purity ring is a personal one, and celebrities may have their own individual reasons for choosing to do so.",
